extends layout

block content
  div.account-detail-card
    div.account-header
      h3 Multi-Factor Authentication Required
      span.account-status Security

    div.mfa-message
      p To edit your profile, you must complete multi-factor authentication (MFA).

      p If you haven't enrolled in MFA yet, please contact your administrator or set up MFA in your Okta account settings.

      h4 Why is MFA required?
      ul
        li Protects your account from unauthorized changes
        li Verifies your identity before sensitive operations
        li Required by security policy for profile modifications

      div.mfa-actions
        a.btn.btn-bank(href="/stepup-mfa") Try MFA Again
        a.btn.btn-secondary(href="/profile") Back to Profile
